name: Hanna Bermann
description: I’m a very normal girl in most ways. I’m not really looking for a relationship. I’m looking for fun! I love going out dancing and drinking and meeting lots of new people. Looks aren’t everything to me, I’m more about personality. If you are a funny, nice guy that is exciting that’s all I need. You better be able to keep up with me in every way. I have a large appetite for fun and well you know haha.i love to see people around me happy and smiling.it make me feel good and relieves stress… 🙂
